}

What is the functionality of the following piece of code?
public void function(Object item)
{
Node temp=new Node(item,trail);
if(isEmpty())
{
head.setNext(temp);
temp.setNext(trail);
}
else
{
Node cur=head.getNext();
while(cur.getNext()!=trail)
{
cur=cur.getNext();
}
cur.setNext(temp);
}
